  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-chat gap-4" data-controller="workspace" data-workspace-id="<%= workspace.to_param %>">
    <%= render "chats/chat", workspace: workspace %>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4" id="<%= dom_id(workspace, :lists) %>" data-target="workspace.lists">
      <div class="any-banner mb-4" role="alert" data-controller="banner" data-banner-id="todo">
        <svg data-action="click->banner#close" class="any-banner--btn" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path class="heroicon-ui" d="M5 3h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5c0-1.1.9-2 2-2zm0 2v14h14V5H5zm8.41 7l1.42 1.41a1 1 0 1 1-1.42 1.42L12 13.4l-1.41 1.42a1 1 0 1 1-1.42-1.42L10.6 12l-1.42-1.41a1 1 0 1 1 1.42-1.42L12 10.6l1.41-1.42a1 1 0 1 1 1.42 1.42L13.4 12z"/></svg>
        <p class="font-bold">TODOs with live updates</p>
        <p>
          This part of the app implements a typical TODO application backed by REST API.
          It is spiced with <em>cables</em> to synchronize updates between the connected clients.
        </p>
        <br/>
        <p>Check out <code>ListsController</code> and <code>ItemsController</code> classes.</p>
      </div>
      <%= render workspace.lists %>
      <%= render "lists/new", workspace: workspace %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
